MODULES:


plot.ss

Provides the basic functionality required to create plots.
provides functions to plot and create renderers, as well 
as the usefull math functions from math.ss


view.ss

Provides access to the view% classes, nessisary in creating your own 
renderers or extending the views.

renderer-helpers.ss

Provides functions usefull in creating your own renderers.
Not documented yet


private modules

syntax.ss 

contains macros used in creating some of the functions.


renderers.ss

contains the built-in renderers. 


math.ss

contains a few useufull math functions.